{"type":"message","id":"4470e6be","parentId":"b6a9a453","timestamp":"2026-06-13T15:18:12.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"private async void browser_to_camera():\n    try {\n        while True:\n            data = await websocket.receive()\n            if data[\"type\"] == \"websocket.receive\":\n                if \"text\" in data:\n                    await cam_ws.send(data[\"text\"])\n                elif \"bytes\" in data:\n                    await cam_ws.send(data[\"bytes\"])\n            elif data[\"type\"] == \"websocket.disconnect\":\n                break\n    except (websockets.exceptions.ConnectionClosed, WebSocketDisconnect):\n        pass\n\n    async def camera_to_browser():\n        try:\n            async for msg in cam_ws:\n                if isinstance(msg, str):\n                    await websocket.send_text(msg)\n                else:\n                    await websocket.send_bytes(msg)\n        except (websockets.exceptions.ConnectionClosed, WebSocketDisconnect):\n            pass\n\n    await asyncio.gather(browser_to_camera(), camera_to_browser())\nexcept websockets.exceptions.InvalidStatus as e:\n    log.error(f\"WS /ws: camera rejected: {e}\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    log.error(f\"WS /ws: proxy failed: {e}\")\n\nlog.info(\"WS /ws: closed\")\n```\n\nфЛЅфИфЛЃч шЁЈцяМхІц WebSocket шПцЅхЄБшДЅяМяМфОхІ `InvalidStatus` хМхИИяМяМцЅхПфМшЎАхНщшЏЏяМфН **фИфМхЏМшДцДфИЊхКчЈхДЉцК**у\n\n`os._exit(0)` чшАчЈхчхЈ `restart_astrohub` хНцАфИ­яМ\nшПцЏхЎхЈфИхчцЈЁху\n\n---\n\n**шЎЉцфЛЌхЎщцЕшЏфИфИщхЏцщЎчхЎхЈцЇяМ**  \n\nфИКфКщЊшЏщхЏцщЎчхЎхЈцЇяМццЗЛх фКщЂхЄчщшЏЏхЄчхцЅхПчЁЎшЎЄцКхЖу\n\nхГфНП `delayed_exit` хНцАцЇшЁ `os._exit(0)` хМКхЖщхКяМчБфКццшПцЅщНхЈ `try-except` хфИ­хЄчяМ\nхКчЈфИфМх  WebSocket щшЏЏхДЉцКу\n\n**чЛшЎКяМ**  \n- WebSocket щшЏЏфИфМхЏМшДхКчЈхДЉцК  \n- щх